            <span class="who">
                <span class="">Dimitri Odinets</span>:
            </span>
            <span class="utterance" who="odinetsD" start="2000.887" end="x">Unfortunately there were such Russians, but I must state that among the intelligentsia, the workers with the pen such as scientists, writers there were no such people.</span>
        </li>
                <li>
            <span class="who">
                <span class="">David Boder</span>:
            </span>
